an></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 0px 1.8em; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">动力强劲效率高<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180503/1-1P5031104524S.gif\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 269px; height: 200px;\" /></span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　独立研发的powertec发动机，动力强劲</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　最大功率383KW，最大扭矩2502N&middot;m</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　爬坡、加速性能大幅度提升</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　国内最大功率ZF变速器，确保最佳行驶性</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　顶尖的电子技术，燃油经济性更高</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　且完全满足国家排放标准<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/20/4.jpeg\" /><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180503/1-1P503110405524.gif\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; width: 269px; height: 200px;\" /></span><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　有安全感</span></strong></div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　耐久可靠超安全<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180503/1-1P5031104524S.gif\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; width: 269px; height: 200px;\" /></span><br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　通过了全世界最严苛的欧洲安全法</span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　材质优良的高强度底盘构造+紧急转向系统</span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　确保行车安全有效提高</span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　可靠刹车片+ABS装置+ASR驱动防滑系统</span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　紧急情况下制动能力更强<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/20/5.jpeg\" /></span><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　除此之外，四川现代始终坚持品质第一</span></div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　客户至上的理念并实施100万公里保修政策</span></div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　将卓越品质与贴心服务完美结合</span></div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　力争为每一位用户送上最好的用车体验</span></div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　面对这样的创虎，你服不服？</span></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n</source></source></source></source></source>', '50', '0', '0', '1525927907', '43');
INSERT INTO `bio_article` VALUES ('13', '如何选择一辆安全性能好的重卡？', '安全性能好的重卡', '赚钱很重要，生命安全更重要！所以，通常在选择购车时，车辆安全性往往是大家最关心的问题！那么如何选择一辆安全性能好的重卡？今天小编为大家推荐的是四川现代创虎重卡！', 'admin', '/public/uploads/trucksfamily/23/1-lp.gif', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　赚钱很重要，生命安全更重要！所以，通常在选择购车时，车辆安全性往往是大家最关心的问题！那么如何选择一辆安全性能好的重卡？今天小编为大家推荐的是四川现代创虎重卡！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　创虎安全性能究竟如何？光听别人说是不行的，必须用事实说话。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　下面小编就为大家带来了创虎碰撞实验的视频，让你一睹究竟（点击视频，见证这触目惊心的一刻）</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/23/1.gif\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　这一下，创虎撞得可是不轻</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　但是，车主没事！</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　这是创虎撞车时的慢动作回放，从撞车后完好无损的驾驶员足以看出创虎的安全性能有多可靠，那么，它是如何做到的呢？下面由小编为您揭秘：</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　1、高强度钢车身&mdash;&mdash;铜墙铁壁护身</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　从视频可以看出，发生碰撞后，创虎车身几乎保持原状。因为它应用框架结构驾驶室，大量采用高张力钢，且增加车顶加强筋数量，有效确保了车头发生猛烈碰撞或者受到大力挤压时不变形，防止驾驶员在事故中身体受到挤压。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/23/2.jpeg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　2、贴心安全配置&mdash;&mdash;紧急气囊护头</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　碰撞发生后，安全气囊第一时间迅速弹出，保护头部不受撞击，方向盘前倾，确保胸腔不受挤压，防止驾驶员出现窒息情况，同时，驾驶室整体有向后移动的趋势，有效地缓解了冲击力。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/23/3.jpeg\" /></span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　3、卓越制动性能&mdash;&mdash;降低事故几率</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　除此之外，创虎还拥有卓越的制动性能。耐久可靠的刹车片，同级车型少有的延迟解除驻车制动技术，标配的ABS防抱死系统，JAKE发动机制动等都大大地提高了创虎的安全性能。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/23/4.jpeg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　创行天下，虎啸九州！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　创虎常伴左右，给你至臻安全保护！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/weixin.gif\" style=\"width: 322px; height: 522px;\" /></span></div>\r\n', '172', '0', '0', '1533087268', '43');
INSERT INTO `bio_article` VALUES ('14', '看创虎寒区版如何征服冰天雪地', '创虎寒区版', '每年到了冬天卡友们出车频率就变得越来越少了特别是温度极低的北方地区，为什么？因为害怕……害怕路况差，驾驶技术不过关？都是老司机，怎么可能？害怕外面太冷，身体受不了？不是，车上都装有空调那到底在害怕什么呢？', 'admin', '/public/uploads/trucksfamily/24/1.jpeg', '<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　每年到了冬天</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　卡友们出车频率就变得越来越少了</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　特别是温度极低的北方地区，为什么？</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　因为害怕&hellip;&hellip;</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/24/1.jpeg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　害怕路况差，驾驶技术不过关？都是老司机，怎么可能</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　害怕外面太冷，身体受不了？不是，车上都装有空调</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　那到底在害怕什么呢？</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　<strong>害怕燃油凝结</strong>，天气变冷，车子面临的考验也愈加严峻</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　每次出车前不仅要热车，以防止润滑油粘滞导致发动机损坏加剧！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　<strong>还要考虑油箱加油的问题</strong>，以防加错了油，过冷导致燃油凝结，车辆无法启动！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/24/2.jpeg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　<strong>那么怎么办？</strong>不出车在家空等也赚不到钱！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　不用急，全新创虎寒区版来帮你！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　<strong>创虎采用回油加热方式及双燃料油箱</strong>，可实现寒区不同标号燃油的加注，根据实际情况切换使用不同的燃油，有效避免燃油结冰！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/24/3.jpeg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　害怕尿素凝结</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　当车辆行驶到北方极寒地区时</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　通常情况，<strong>尿素在零下11摄氏度会结冰</strong></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　使车辆不能进行正常的尿素喷射</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　导致车辆故障以及排放无法满足法规要求</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/24/6.jpeg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　<strong>怎么办？</strong>全新创虎寒区版来帮你</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　创虎尿素系统采用电加热方式</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　解决尿素结冰现象</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　有效防止因为尿素结冰而导致出现</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　输出扭矩与车速受限等问题</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/24/7.jpeg\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 561px;\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　害怕停车等待</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　天气变冷，停车等待成为大家害怕的问题</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　不启动车辆，空调无法工作</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　坐在车上冷得难受</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　启动车辆，费油耗电</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　出车成本猛增，心里又感觉不划算！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/24/4.jpeg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　不用急！全新创虎寒区版来帮你</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　创虎，拥有独立风暖设计</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　无需启动车辆即可加热室内空气</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　通过燃烧室燃料与吸入的室外空气进行燃烧</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　并将产生的热量传递给室内空气</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　使驾驶室保持温暖</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/public/uploads/trucksfamily/24/5.jpeg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　跟着全新创虎寒区版一起挑战冰雪</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　　即刻出发，不用怕！</span></strong></div>\r\n', '88', '0', '0', '1525927985', '43');
