INSERT INTO `bio_article` VALUES ('52', '车主说 | 全程记录我的选车经历', '车主说 | 全程记录我的选车经历', '随着物流行业的迅猛发展，各种各样的货车层出不穷，在这个“选车难”的时代，如何才能快速选中一款最适合自己的车辆呢？今天，小编发现一位卡友在卡车之家论坛上跟大家讲述了他的选车经历。', 'admin', '/public/uploads/allimg/180612/1-1P6121G242432-lp.jpg', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	</div>\r\n<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n	<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n		<section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n			<section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;border-width: 2px;border-style: dotted;border-color: rgb(210, 218, 218);padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								随着物流行业的迅猛发展，各种各样的货车层出不穷，在这个<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;选车难&rdquo;</strong>的时代，<strong>如何才能快速选中一款最适合自己的车辆呢？</strong></p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								今天，小编发现一位卡友在卡车之家论坛上跟大家讲述了他的选车经历。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<img data-=\"\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.6980108\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"553\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180612/1-1P6121G242432.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: visible !important; width: 556px; height: 386px;\" /></section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								他是一名来自重庆的年轻小伙，也是一名新晋的四川现代盛图车主，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">卡车之家论坛<span style=\"color: rgb(252, 7, 7);box-sizing: border-box;\">ID：九爷儿</span></strong>。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								从准备买车到现在，经过近一个月的精挑细选，他终于选定了盛图。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								他表示，要买一款适合自己的好车，是一个漫长的过程，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">必须注意以下几点之后，才有可能成功</strong>。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: 12%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								<section style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-bottom: 3px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n									<section style=\"border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(121, 5, 5);background-color: rgb(121, 5, 5);display: inline-block;width: 1.8em;height: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;border-radius: 100%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n										<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n											<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">01</strong></p>\r\n									</section>\r\n								</section>\r\n							</section>\r\n						</section>\r\n						<section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: 88%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								<section style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n									<section style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n										<section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(121, 5, 5);margin-bottom: 0.25em;padding-left: 5px;padding-right: 5px;font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n											<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n												<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">认准买车的用途</strong></p>\r\n										</section>\r\n										<section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;widt