INSERT INTO `bio_article` VALUES ('53', '车主说 | 我的创虎520湖州——广州往返之行，这油耗我很满意', '车主,说,我的,创虎,520,湖州,—,广州,往返,', '俗话说，酒香不怕巷子深。作为重卡先锋，近日四川现代创虎凭借其卓越的产品性能以及抢眼的高效运输表现，再一次赢得了广大卡友的高度认可，在论坛上引来好评不断，一起来看看吧。', 'admin', '/public/uploads/allimg/180612/1-1P6121H2204P-lp.jpg', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	</div>\r\n<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n	<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n		<section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n			<section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;padding: 10px;background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								俗话说，酒香不怕巷子深。作为重卡先锋，近日四川现代创虎凭借其卓越的产品性能以及抢眼的高效运输表现，再一次赢得了广大卡友的高度认可，在论坛上引来好评不断，一起来看看吧。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<img data-=\"\" data-fail=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180612/1-1P6121H2204P.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: visible !important; width: 640px; height: 480px;\" /></section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								他是一名创虎车主，ID小辉辉啊（<span style=\"color: rgb(5, 40, 140);box-sizing: border-box;\">以下简称小辉</span>），<strong>他</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">拥有一辆最新款520马力创虎重卡，配备采埃孚16挡变速箱，速比为3.417</strong>。由于爱车一直以来的优异表现，忍不住第一次在论坛上发帖，讲述了湖州&mdash;&mdash;广州往返之行中创虎给自己留下的深刻印象。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<img data-=\"\" data-fail=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.0640625\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180612/1-1P6121H22V62.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: visible !important; width: 640px; height: 681px;\" /></section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<section style=\"width: 45px;height: 5px;line-height: 5px;background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</section>\r\n							<section style=\"margin-top: -3px;margin-bottom: -3px;transform: rotate(0deg);border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n									<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">牢固车架，超强承载</strong></p>\r\n							</section>\r\n							<section style=\"width: 45px;height: 5px;margin-left: auto;line-height: 5px;background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</section>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								此次从湖州到广州，小辉师傅的创虎重卡<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">净装货38吨</strong>，加上车皮16吨，共54吨，返程时，则拉了<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">40吨的板材</strong>，充分展示出了创虎重卡超强的承载能力。一路上，经过高速，也走过山坡，但是车辆开起来十分稳定，令小辉师傅非常满意。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<img data-=\"\" data-fail=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.6765625\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180612/1-1P6121H23A18.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: visible !important; width: 640px; height: 433px;\" /></section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								创虎，<span style=\"color: rgb(252, 7, 7);box-sizing: border-box;\">框架式车身采用进口高张力钢制成</span>，高强度钢比率达到50%，防撞击性能更好，拥有一次性辊压成型高张力钢车架，<span style=\"color: rgb(252, 7, 7);box-sizing: border-box;\">抗拉强度高达780Mpa</span>，承载能力更强，使用寿命大于150万公里。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<img data-=\"\" data-fail=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.7953125\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180612/1-1P6121H243V5.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: visible !important; width: 640px; height: 509px;\" /></section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<section style=\"width: 45px;height: 5px;margin-left: auto;line-height: 5px;background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</section>\r\n							<section style=\"margin-top: -3px;margin-bottom: -3px;transform: rotate(0deg);border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n									<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">强劲动力，节油高效</strong></p>\r\n							</section>\r\n							<section style=\"width: 45px;height: 5px;line-height: 5px;background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</section>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								更令小辉师傅喜出望外的，是货运途中爱车创虎高效经济的节油性能。<strong>在40吨的重载情况下</strong>，创虎不仅表现出了强劲的动力，油耗方面也控制得十分到位，<span style=\"color: rgb(252, 7, 7);box-sizing: border-box;\">高速路段，百公里油耗为32.3L，即使爬坡路段，百公里油耗也只增加了2.3L，达到34.6L</span>，让小辉师傅感到非常惊喜。</p>\r\n						</section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<img data-=\"\" data-fail=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.7953125\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180612/1-1P6121H2512S.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: visible !important; width: 640px; height: 509px;\" /></section>\r\n					</section>\r\n				</section>\r\n				<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n					<section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n						<section style=\"font-size: 13px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n							<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n								<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">高速路段百公里油耗</str