lay: inline-block;width: 95%;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: 70%;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 66, 87);text-align: justify;line-height: 1.8;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n											每一次爸爸回家，都会和妈妈一起给大家做好吃的，还会给妈妈买好看的衣服，所以，妈妈总跟我说，要做一个像爸爸一样可靠的人。</p></section></section></section></section><section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: 20%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 65%;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img _width=\"100%\" data-=\"\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" data-ratio=\"3.0705128\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"156\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180620/1-1P620092S1H1.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; width: 50px; height: 154px; visibility: visible !important;\"/></section></section></section></section></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: -5px 0% 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"background-color: rgb(44, 90, 160);height: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &