.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n					&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">俗话说，<span style=\"color: rgb(246, 28, 19);font-size: 21px;box-sizing: border-box;\">虎</span>父无犬子</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n					作为创虎车主，有一个这么懂事的孩子</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n					你是不是该感到非常地欣慰？<br/><br/><img data-=\"\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.50074294205052\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"673\" src=\"/public/uploads/allimg/180620/1-1P620092642206.jpg\" style=\"visibility: visible !important;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n					但是，如果刚过的儿童节你没能陪孩子</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n					那么，今天早点回家陪他吧</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n					让他感受到更多的父爱</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">最后，祝天下卡友父亲节快乐！</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>', '79', '0', '0', '1529458210', '43');
